      "title": "Shop home FAQ",
      "description": "FAQ section on shop home",
      "page": "shop-home",
      "cardType": "more-info",
      "cards": [
        {
          "content": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <title>Accordion FAQ</title>\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <!-- Tailwind CSS CDN for styling (optional, remove if not needed) -->\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script>\n    <script>\n      document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function () {\n        const accordion = document.getElementById(\"faq-accordion\");\n        accordion.addEventListener(\"click\", function (event) {\n          const button = event.target.closest(\".accordion-toggle\");\n          if (!button) return;\n\n          const content =\n            button.parentElement.querySelector(\".accordion-content\");\n          const isHidden = content.classList.contains(\"hidden\");\n\n          // Close all\n          accordion\n            .querySelectorAll(\".accordion-content\")\n            .forEach((el) => el.classList.add(\"hidden\"));\n          accordion.querySelectorAll(\".accordion-toggle\").forEach((el) => {\n            el.classList.remove(\"font-semibold\");\n            const icon = el.querySelector(\".accordion-icon\");\n            icon && icon.classList.remove(\"rotate-180\");\n          });\n\n          // Open clicked\n          if (isHidden) {\n            content.classList.remove(\"hidden\");\n            button.classList.add(\"font-semibold\");\n            const icon = button.querySelector(\".accordion-icon\");\n            icon && icon.classList.add(\"rotate-180\");\n          }\n        });\n      });\n    </script>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <div class=\"accordion space-y-4 max-w-xl mx-auto\" id=\"faq-accordion\">\n      <h2\n        class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-10\"\n        style=\"font-size: 30px; margin-bottom: 2rem\"\n      >\n        Got questions?\n      </h2>\n      <!-- Accordion Item 1 -->\n      <div class=\"accordion-item !mt-0 font-normal\" style=\"margin-top: 0!important;\">\n        <button\n          class=\"accordion-toggle w-full flex items-center justify-between py-4 text-left font-semibold\"\n        >\n          <span class=\"text-base\">\n            When do the months start to run during which I can use the service\n            in a position without additional payment?\n          </span>\n          <svg\n            class=\"accordion-icon w-6 h-6 text-gray-600 transition-transform duration-300 rotate-180\"\n            fill=\"none\"\n            stroke=\"currentColor\"\n            stroke-width=\"2\"\n            viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\n          >\n            <path\n              stroke-linecap=\"round\"\n              stroke-linejoin=\"round\"\n              d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"\n            />\n          </svg>\n        </button>\n        <hr />\n        <div class=\"accordion-content py-4 bg-white text-sm text-gray-600\">\n          From the date of signing the contract of your subscription plan.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Accordion Item 2 -->\n      <div class=\"accordion-item !mt-0 font-normal\" style=\"margin-top: 0!important;\">\n        <button\n          class=\"accordion-toggle w-full flex items-center justify-between py-4 text-left\"\n        >\n          <span class=\"text-base\"\n            >Do I have to pay extra for the services?</span\n          >\n          <svg\n            class=\"accordion-icon w-6 h-6 text-gray-600 transition-transform duration-300\"\n            fill=\"none\"\n            stroke=\"currentColor\"\n            stroke-width=\"2\"\n            viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\n          >\n            <path\n              stroke-linecap=\"round\"\n              stroke-linejoin=\"round\"\n              d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"\n            />\n          </svg>\n        </button>\n        <hr />\n        <div\n          class=\"accordion-content hidden py-4 bg-white text-sm text-gray-600\"\n        >\n          Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting\n          industry.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Accordion Item 3 -->\n      <div class=\"accordion-item !mt-0 font-normal\" style=\"margin-top: 0!important;\">\n        <button\n          class=\"accordion-toggle w-full flex items-center justify-between py-4 text-left\"\n        >\n          <span class=\"text-base\"\n            >How do I manage my digital services positions?</span\n          >\n          <svg\n            class=\"accordion-icon w-6 h-6 text-gray-600 transition-transform duration-300\"\n            fill=\"none\"\n            stroke=\"currentColor\"\n            stroke-width=\"2\"\n            viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\n          >\n            <path\n              stroke-linecap=\"round\"\n              stroke-linejoin=\"round\"\n              d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"\n            />\n          </svg>\n        </button>\n        <hr />\n        <div\n          class=\"accordion-content hidden py-4 bg-white text-sm text-gray-600\"\n        >\n          Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting\n          industry.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Accordion Item 4 -->\n      <div class=\"accordion-item !mt-0 font-normal\" style=\"margin-top: 0!important;\">\n        <button\n          class=\"accordion-toggle w-full flex items-center justify-between py-4 text-left\"\n        >\n          <span class=\"text-base\"\n            >I can't fill my digital services position</span\n          >\n          <svg\n            class=\"accordion-icon w-6 h-6 text-gray-600 transition-transform duration-300\"\n            fill=\"none\"\n            stroke=\"currentColor\"\n            stroke-width=\"2\"\n            viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\n          >\n            <path\n              stroke-linecap=\"round\"\n              stroke-linejoin=\"round\"\n              d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"\n            />\n          </svg>\n        </button>\n        <hr />\n        <div\n          class=\"accordion-content hidden py-4 bg-white text-sm text-gray-600\"\n        >\n          Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting\n          industry.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </body>\n</html>\n",
